- [ ] Integration test: graceful shutdown completes in-flight requests
- [ ] Integration test: force close after timeout
- [ ] Lab runtime: deterministic shutdown sequence
- [ ] Stress test: shutdown under load

## Files to Create/Modify
- src/server/connection.rs: ConnectionManager, ConnectionGuard
- src/server/shutdown.rs: ShutdownSignal, ShutdownPhase
- src/server/mod.rs: module structure

